title: Cosmos.Ep5.Blues for a Red Planet.divx
description:
Episode 5: Blues for a Red Planet

Is there life on Mars? Dr. Sagan takes viewers on a never-before-seen
look at the red planet through the eyes of science fiction authors and
then through the unblinking eyes of two Viking spacecraft that have sent 
thousands of pictures of the stunning Martian landscape back to Earth
since 1976.

Digitally Remastered
Audio: 6 Channel Stereo (English)
Video: 4:3  640x480 (Divx)
